Police Minister Bheki Cele has released the crime statistics for the fourth quarter of 2021/2022. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Police Minister Bheki Cele says majority of kidnapping cases reported to the police came from Gauteng. He says most of the kidnapping cases were hijacking, robbery, and rape-related. READ: Violent crime increases in first part of the year, stats reveal Cele released the crime statistics for the fourth quarter of 2021/2022 on Friday. The murder rate increased by 22.2 percent. 